snippet.title: Grant Hodges
snippet.description:
Just some pretentious twenty-something with a film degree and not much else to show for it. Well... except this channel. Where for the low, low price of just a YouTube subscription, you can be subjected to my inner thoughts while watching TV and films!

Letterboxd: https://letterboxd.com/ghodges96/

Instagram Account: https://www.instagram.com/granthodgesphotography/
